headline.print_headline: Leeds Sack Manager Hockaday After Six Games
headline.main: Leeds Sack Manager Hockaday After Six Games

lead_paragraph: Leeds United have sacked manager David Hockaday after only six games in charge, the Championship (second tier) club announced on Thursday.
